<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Câu_lạc_bộ_bóng_đá_Manchester_United"><span id="C.C3.A2u_l.E1.BA.A1c_b.E1.BB.99_b.C3.B3ng_.C4.91.C3.A1_Manchester_United"></span>Câu lạc bộ bóng đá Manchester United</h3></div>
<table class="wikitable">

